<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Appointment Cancellation Notice</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
    }
    h2 {
      color: #dc3545;
    }
    .appointment-details {
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 15px;
      border: 1px solid #f5c6cb;
      background-color: #f8d7da;
    }
    .appointment-details strong {
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .note {
      font-style: italic;
      color: #555;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Appointment Cancellation Notice</h2>
    <p>Hello {{ patientName }},</p>
    <p>We regret to inform you that your scheduled medical appointment has been <strong>cancelled</strong>.</p>

    <div class="appointment-details">
      <p><strong>Time:</strong> {{ appointmentTime }}</p>
      <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{ appointmentDate }}</p>
      {{#if doctorName}}
      <p><strong>Doctor:</strong> {{ doctorName }}</p>
      {{/if}}
      {{#if appointmentAddress}}
      <p><strong>Location:</strong> {{ appointmentAddress }}</p>
      {{/if}}
      {{#if reason}}
      <p class="note"><strong>Cancellation Reason:</strong> {{ reason }}</p>
      {{/if}}
    </div>

    <p>If you have any questions or would like to reschedule, please contact us or visit our online booking system.</p>

    <p>Best regards,</p>
    <p>Clinic Appointment System</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
